<section id="fs-id1850777">
<title>Velocity</title>

    <para id="import-auto-id1757608">Your notion of velocity is probably the same as its scientific definition. You know that if you have a large displacement in a small amount of time you have a large velocity, and that velocity has units of distance divided by time, such as miles per hour or kilometers per hour. </para>
    <note xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" id="fs-id3597968">
<label/>
